    {
      "id": "dus-j4wZyWmMpISXFRtL_",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -6555.986007046681,
      "y": 1239.7308009671722,
      "width": 782.2398071289062,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "GXYsnwj4GAkLi091KxNrx",
        "6MjBh4fXOPU0AHEr1v9bA"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cDIJ",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1597982313,
      "version": 204,
      "versionNonce": 1319430414,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772853188926,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- V exchange(V v)：等待另一个线程到达此交换点（除非当前线程被中断），然后将给定\n的对象传送给该线程，并接收该线程的对象。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- V exchange(V v)：等待另一个线程到达此交换点（除非当前线程被中断），然后将给定的对象传送给该线程，并接收该线程的对象。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "f_POEEO2Zq5OEBfbCkBMC",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -6555.986007046681,
      "y": 1305.5865681078694,
      "width": 800,
      "height": 75,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "GXYsnwj4GAkLi091KxNrx",
        "6MjBh4fXOPU0AHEr1v9bA"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "cDIK",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 739078311,
      "version": 185,
      "versionNonce": 155481810,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1772853188926,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- V exchange(V v, long timeout, TimeUnit unit)：等待另一个线程到达此交换点，或者当\n前线程被中断——抛出中断异常；又或者是等候超时——抛出超时异常，然后将给定的对象\n传送给该线程，并接收该线程的对象。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- V exchange(V v, long timeout, TimeUnit unit)：等待另一个线程到达此交换点，或者当前线程被中断——抛出中断异常；又或者是等候超时——抛出超时异常，然后将给定的对象传送给该线程，并接收该线程的对象。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "ZObtw-qZY5cS8k6ddjjtM",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -6555.986007046681,
      "y": 1396.4423352485662,
      "width": 841.7998046875,
      "height": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
