      "text": "- protected boolean onAdvance(int phase，int registeredParties)类似CyclicBarrier的触发\n命令，通过重写该方法来增加阶段到达动作，该方法返回true将终结Phaser对象。",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- protected boolean onAdvance(int phase，int registeredParties)类似CyclicBarrier的触发命令，通过重写该方法来增加阶段到达动作，该方法返回true将终结Phaser对象。",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
